        <section class="container">
                    <h1 class="u-entryTitle">This is the Army’s plan to stop physically breaking so many of its soldiers</h1>
          <p class="Article-excerpt">
  “My sergeants major right now, they hurt. Their bodies hurt."
</p>

<p class="Article-author">
                    By
                              <a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/author/haley-britzky/"
             rel="author"
             class="fn author-link">
            Haley Britzky
          </a>
                
              |
    <span class="Article-dateTime">
    <time datetime="2021-10-27T12:02:48-04:00">
    Updated Oct 27, 2021 12:02 PM EDT
    </time>
  </span>
</p>
<ul class="Article-categories">
      <li>
      <a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/category/news/">
        News
      </a>
    </li>
                                                                                    <li>
            <a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/category/military-life/">
              Military Life
            </a>
          </li>
                        </ul>
        </section>
      </header>
    
          <figure class="Article-thumbnail orgnc-SingleImage orgnc-SingleImage--center orgnc-SingleImage--hasCaption">
                    <div class="orgnc-SingleImage-wrapper"><img fetchpriority="high" width="1440" height="810" src="https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg?auto=webp&amp;width=1440&amp;height=810" srcset="https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg?auto=webp&optimize=high&width=360 360w,https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg?auto=webp&optimize=high&width=390 390w,https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg?auto=webp&optimize=high&width=412 412w,https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg?auto=webp&optimize=high&width=1200 1200w,https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg?auto=webp&optimize=high&width=1366 1366w,https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg?auto=webp&optimize=high&width=1440 1440w" class="orgnc-SingleImage-image Article-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Paratroopers assigned to 2nd Brigade Combat Team, 82nd Airborne Division, utilize the physical training strength and conditioning coaches at the Falcon Holistic Health and Fitness Center (H2F) on October, 18, 2021 at Fort Bragg, North Carolina. (Staff Sgt. Andrew Mallett/U.S. Army)" decoding="async" srcset="https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training.jpg 1920w, https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training-300x169.jpg 300w, https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training-768x432.jpg 768w, https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2021/10/27/2nd-BCT-training-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px" data-dimension="landscape" /></div><figcaption class="orgnc-SingleImage-caption">Paratroopers assigned to 2nd Brigade Combat Team, 82nd Airborne Division, utilize the physical training strength and conditioning coaches at the Falcon Holistic Health and Fitness Center (H2F) on October, 18, 2021 at Fort Bragg, North Carolina. (Staff Sgt. Andrew Mallett/U.S. Army).</figcaption></figure>    
    <section class="Article-body">
      <section class="Article-content">
                  
                      <section class="Article-socialShare">
